title: The best Locksmith services in the Fremont Metro area
name: The best Locksmith services in the Fremont Metro area

properties.name: Multi  Locksmith Rancho Cordova- Lock Change, Repair & Installation
properties.description: Posted by Hayleighjerome 10923 Progress Ct P.O box 3138, Rancho Cordova, 95741, CABeing the flake I can sometimes be, I recently locked my keys in my apartment. It was around 9am on my way to work. Frustrated and getting wet (as of course, it was raining that afternoon), I made it to the job, and logged onto the net for a locksmith. This was the one and only guy I called to Multi Locksmith Rancho Cordova- Lock Change, Repair & Installation, mostly because he\'s located nearby, and I hoped he would get there fast. He told me to give him a ring at (916) 244-3931 about 1/2 hour before I got home, which I did. He told me he would arrive in 25 minutes, and I told him I\'d be at the bar down the block so to call my cell first. When he arrived the entire ordeal lasted only about 10 minutes, all the while we discussed some spiritual stuff. He asked me if I wanted him to do a lock re-key, but since my lost keys were inside, I told him it wasn’t necessary. Once inside he made me show him proof that I lived there, and he charged me 0 (which he quoted me on the phone). I accidentally gave him a 00, and he saw that, and handed me 0 back. So the guy\'s honest too. I\'ll call him if I\'m in a bind again, although the next morning I made a ton of extra sets of keys.
